title: The Rose Blooms
body:
read it on the AO3 at http://bit.ly/2PWHpD8

by Heather_Hearts

“I think we’ve both been alone for a long time, (y/n).”

Ten years ago, you woke up in a world where nothing felt familiar. Waking up on a strange planet, with no memories, and only a small device. After making your way across the galaxy, searching for years and finding that nothing helps you to remember, you decide to join The New Order as a storm trooper, to fight for order and control in the galaxy.

But now it appears that the Commander of The New Order has taken an interest in you.

What will bloom between the two of you I wonder?
